<strong>Aim:</strong></p>

<p>To develop a community device that can be used by people without disabilities, but is accessible to wheelchair users, particularly people with paraplegia</p>

<p><strong>Summary:</strong></p>

<p>Developed the complete electronics module of the proof of concept prototype, starting with a functioning mechanical prototype, having worked on features like:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Wireless speed control</li>
  <li>A ‚Äúpush to start‚Äù feature</li>
  <li>Wireless data logging</li>
  <li>Mechanical design synthesis of a locking mechanism</li>
</ul>

